cc:Work.dc:title: Kitten holding a sign
cc:Work.dc:description: This is a picture of a kitten wearing a "sandwich sign" bearing the words "Oh, Meow". It comes from the dedication page "Dorothy and the Wizard in Oz" (1908). The kitten is probably Eureka the Pink Kitten, from the story. You can get the book here: \n \nhttp://www.archive.org/details/dorothywizardino00baum2
